  missionTitle: Vidhansabha Ki Raah
  completionTitle: CHAPTER 9 COMPLETE
  completionMessage: Ward seva ab constituency organization ban chuki hai. Reach,
    unity aur readiness ka har number save ho gaya.
  chapterNumber: 9
  nextChapterScene: 
  introTitle: CHAPTER 9 / VIDHANSABHA KI RAAH
  introMessage: Ward ki jeet ko constituency bhar ke accountable public network mein
    badlo.
  objectives:
  - {fileID: 992218402}
  - {fileID: 825100446}
  - {fileID: 1462819198}
  - {fileID: 974090269}
  - {fileID: 519279468}
  - {fileID: 1954439793}
  - {fileID: 179685999}
  - {fileID: 1264551911}
  - {fileID: 688555790}
  - {fileID: 1176484415}
  - {fileID: 879065789}
  - {fileID: 192077233}
  objectiveLabels:
  - Citizen panel se corrected 100-day audit closure lein
  - Independent desk par candidate eligibility aur disclosures verify karein
  - Urban water camp mein ward-wise complaints aur deadlines lock karein
  - Youth ke saath verified apprenticeship aur stipend plan banayein
  - Rural irrigation aur paperwork camp mein receipt-based help karein
  - Shanti aur neutral police liaison ke saath safety route audit karein
  - Issue-based civic coalition ka common charter agree karein
  - Assets, donations aur measurable promises ka public disclosure karein
  - Ground jan-sabha ya high-pressure dhol roadshow mein decision lein
  - Fictional opposition ko source-backed public debate mein jawab dein
  - Privacy-safe booth map aur volunteer shifts lock karein
  - Independent panel par computed MLA nomination score dekhein
  milestoneSteps: 030000000600000009000000
  milestoneTitles:
  - CLEAN RECORD VERIFIED
  - URBAN-RURAL ROUTE ACTIVE
  - PUBLIC CANDIDACY READY
  milestoneMessages:
  - Audit, eligibility aur urban water camp complete. Expansion ab verified record
    par khadi hai.
  - Youth, rural paperwork aur safety route linked hain. Ab issue-based coalition
    banani hai.
  - Coalition, disclosures aur outreach strategy locked. Debate aur booth map nomination
    decide karenge.
